ch.pschatzmann.jflightcontroller4pi.integration

Class DatagramReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.pschatzmann.jflightcontroller4pi.integration.DatagramReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IFrequency, IDevice, ISensor

    public class DatagramReader
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISensor
    Read values from a UDP Port (e.g. from JSBSim) into the ParameterStore. We can support multiple protocols (by setting the input processors. If nothing is defined we set up the default protocols.
    Author:
    pschatzmann
